{"tid":1171649,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嫌老婆啪啪啪時衣服脫太慢　議員竟揮拳揍她","createTime":"2019-05-26T00:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T22:07:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de9eea6e57f65ea68c5f867cfe837aced2798047","tid":1171649,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:46:17.000Z","msg":"美國美國密西西比州共和黨參議員，被指控酒醉後毆打他妻子，因為他嫌要跟妻子啪啪啪時，妻子衣服脫太慢。<br />\n據《BBC》報導，58瑞的麥克勞德(Douglas McLeod)，18日遭指控家庭暴力而被逮，他在該州的同黨同僚指出，如果事情屬實的話，麥克勞德應該立刻辭職。據悉，當警方抵達麥克勞德的家中時，他喝得相當醉，且手上還拿著酒精飲料、走路東倒西歪，當警方指他被控家庭暴力時，麥克勞德還說「你在開玩笑嗎？」<br />\n一名女子告訴警員，麥克勞德的老婆滿臉是血地跑進她房間，並且把門鎖上，而麥克勞德開始敲門並威脅說不開門就殺死她們。警方說這對夫妻的臥室有血跡，而起因為麥克勞德想跟老婆啪啪啪時，老婆衣服脫太慢，才火大出手。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190526/640_055740e9009b54654563f4179ebe19a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190526%2F640_055740e9009b54654563f4179ebe19a1.jpg&h=70496c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDouglas McLeod。翻攝自BBC<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190526/640_f5f6b47bc927598161f05f244fa5bba2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190526%2F640_f5f6b47bc927598161f05f244fa5bba2.jpg&h=7fca10dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e24b7144d5d91ca1c0b9101ba496f519dcb01c5","tid":1171649,"uid":17641,"like":18,"dislike":7,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:47:27.000Z","msg":"打得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021016a242a65b09231c1f8870d2188b9729625c","tid":1171649,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T00:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n張圖好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb34d8f73d6848ec1798ac5b8c268db3928790e","tid":1171649,"uid":2267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0210